  "description": "Add Consistent Styling to Embedded Gallery Item Images\n\nUpdate CSS styling for images within embedded gallery items to remove margins and adjust border radius for a flush, seamless appearance.\n\nRequirements:\n- Target selector: .embedded-gallery-item picture img\n- Set margin to 0 on all sides to eliminate any spacing\n- Set border-radius on bottom edges (bottom-left and bottom-right) to 0\n- Preserve any existing border-radius on top edges if present\n- Ensure changes don't break responsive behavior or other gallery layouts\n- Verify styling consistency across different browsers",
